assetProfile.longBusinessSummary: Tritax EuroBox plc invest in and manage a well-diversified portfolio of large, high-quality logistics real estate assets, known as Big Boxes. It seeks to invests in properties fulfilling a key part of the logistics and distribution supply chain for occupiers including retailers, manufacturers and third-party logistics operators. The fund focus on key logistics hubs, which are close to major population centres in Europe's most-established logistics markets and have good availability of labour. It seeks to invest in Foundation assets, Value add assets, Growth covenant assets and strategic land. Tritax EuroBox plc primarily invests across core countries in Continental Europe.
